    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">著裝該護甲時，你的</span><span class=\"1\">AC </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">獲得</span><span class=\"1\">+1 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">加值。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">這身皮甲共有</span><span class=\"1\">3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">發充能，並將於每天黎明時恢復[[/r 1d3]]發充能。當你攻擊並擊中一個失去了任何量生命值的目標時，你可以消耗一發充能，並對該目標額外造成</span><span class=\"1\">[[/r 1d10]]</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">的黯蝕傷害。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></div>",
